<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ZORA | About Us</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.jpg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="middle-nav">
            <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; width: 100px;">
                ABOUT<br>ZORA</div>
            <div class="brand-main">ZORA</div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
                <% if (currentUser) { %>
                    <a href="/logout" style="color: black; font-size: 1.2rem;"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i></a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/login" class="btn-orange">LOGIN</a>
                        <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container" style="max-width: 800px; padding: 10rem 1.5rem;">
        <h1
            style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 6rem; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 0.9; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            A Legacy of <br>Curated Content.</h1>
        <p
            style="font-size: 1.5rem; border-top: var(--border-thick); padding-top: 2rem; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            Zora Archive was established to bridge the gap between fast-paced digital media and the timeless quality of
            print journalism.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.8;">
            We focus on long-form stories, visual essays, and deep-dive research into technology and culture. Our
            platform is built for those who appreciate the art of the written word and the impact of clean, intentional
            design.
        </p>
    </main>

    <footer class="magazine-footer"
        style="padding: 6rem 4% 4rem 4%; background: white; border-top: var(--border-thin);">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div>
                <div class="brand-main"
                    style="font-size: 8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); letter-spacing: -4px; line-height: 0.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    ZORA</div>
                <p style="max-width: 500px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                    Zora is a curated fashion magazine dedicated to high-fashion narratives and architectural design
                    research. Established in 2026, we serve as a definitive resource for curators, designers, and
                    historians seeking the intersection of movement and structure.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4
                    style="font-family: var(--font-heading); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    EDITION 01</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; line-height: 1.8;">
                    MAY 2026 / NEW YORK CITY<br>
                    PUBLISHED BY ZORA MEDIA GROUP<br>
                    PRINTED DIGITALLY WORLDWIDE
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4
                    style="font-family: var(--font-heading); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    NAVIGATION</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <a href="/archive" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">FULL ARCHIVE</a><br>
                    <a href="/contact" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">CONTACT US</a><br>
                    <a href="/home" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">BACK TO FEED</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
            style="margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #aaa; text-transform: uppercase;">
            &copy; 2026 ZORA MAGAZINE. REDEFINING THE DIGITAL NARRATIVE.
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>